chuckeles.sstasker.model.parts

Interface Part

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Generator, OxygenGenerator, PartWithHealth, PartWithoutHealth, Wheel

    public interface Part
    Spaceship part, e. g. and engine, a console, and oxygen generator... Has a reliability, health and whether it is currently functional or not.
